sequenceDiagram
    %% COMP370 Mini Project 2 - Sequence: Startup and Leader Election
    autonumber
    participant S1 as Server 1
    participant S2 as Server 2
    participant S3 as Server 3

    Note over S1,S3: Cluster startup
    S1->>S1: start() launches UDP listener, TCP listener, main loop
    S2->>S2: start() launches UDP listener, TCP listener, main loop
    S3->>S3: start() launches UDP listener, TCP listener, main loop

    loop Tick every 500 ms
      S1->>S1: check role and election timeout
      S2->>S2: check role and election timeout
      S3->>S3: check role and election timeout
    end

    Note over S1: Election timeout expires first
    S1->>S1: startElection()\nrole=CANDIDATE, term++, self-vote, reset timeout
    S1->>S2: RequestVoteArgs(term, candidateId, lastLogIndex, lastLogTerm)
    S1->>S3: RequestVoteArgs(term, candidateId, lastLogIndex, lastLogTerm)

    S2->>S2: handleRequestVote(args)
    S2->>S2: compare term, vote state, and log freshness
    S2-->>S1: RequestVoteResults(term, voteGranted=true)

    S3->>S3: handleRequestVote(args)
    S3->>S3: compare term, vote state, and log freshness
    S3-->>S1: RequestVoteResults(term, voteGranted=true)

    S1->>S1: handleVoteResult(res)\nvotesReceived++
    S1->>S1: majority reached
    S1->>S1: becomeLeader()\ncurrentLeaderId=id, init nextIndex/matchIndex
    Note over S1: Leader elected for current term

    loop Heartbeat / replication cycle
      S1->>S1: sendHeartbeats()
      S1->>S2: AppendEntriesArgs(term, leaderId, prevLogIndex, prevLogTerm, entries?, leaderCommit)
      S1->>S3: AppendEntriesArgs(term, leaderId, prevLogIndex, prevLogTerm, entries?, leaderCommit)

      S2->>S2: handleAppendEntries(args)\nreset timeout, record leader, stay FOLLOWER
      S2-->>S1: AppendEntriesResults(term, success=true)

      S3->>S3: handleAppendEntries(args)\nreset timeout, record leader, stay FOLLOWER
      S3-->>S1: AppendEntriesResults(term, success=true)

      S1->>S1: handleAppendEntriesResult(...)\nupdate follower progress
    end
